Currently, anyone can read the contents of our discussion thread.  However, only those individuals with accounts will be able to post on this board.  It is best if you set up a global account rather than a local account.  There are thousands of EZBoards out there.  Many of them require you to have an account.  Why limit your self?  You will need to come up wth a board name and a password for your account.  Also, either un-check the private box for your e-mail or &quot;enable&quot; the private message status on your account.  Without one or the other, no one will be able to write you or send you PM's.<br>
<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:blue;"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Editing Your EZBoard Profile</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
